  "text": "We highlight that our new expressions in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] are easy to compute since they involve power functions, exponential functions, and hypergeometric functions only. We highlight that the values of these functions, including the hypergeometric function, can be easily computed. Thus, the optimal parameter and the optimal performance presented in Section III-C can be easily obtained. Notably, the derived results in [CITATION_3] and (20) are valid for an arbitrary number of transmit antennas and arbitrary average SNRs.",
